    <div class="gk-tip">
      <strong>How to use this page:</strong> The Constitution has <strong>448 articles</strong> (as amended) in 25 Parts and 12 Schedules. UPSC Prelims tests ~60–80 key articles repeatedly. This cheat sheet covers the highest-frequency articles — learn the article number, the subject, and the exam-critical note column.
